      <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M6 1L11 10H1L6 1Z" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.85)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M6 5V7" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.85)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square"/><circle cx="6" cy="9" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.85)"/></svg>
    </span>
    <span class="announce-text announce-text--desktop">
      Cracked brick &amp; mortar damage worsens every winter — Get a FREE inspection before it's too late
    </span>
    <span class="announce-text announce-text--mobile">
      Free masonry inspection — limited slots
    </span>
    <a href="/contact#form" class="announce-cta" aria-label="Get a free masonry inspection" id="announce-cta-link">Get Free Inspection</a>
